{"title": "Virtues of Mary", "description": "Though we adore God alone and render to Him alone the honor and glory that are due to Him from the creature to the Creator, nevertheless, as part of our worship of God we honor and invoke the friends most dear to Him.  God's own mother is beyond all measure dearer to Him than His friends can be, therefore we venerate Mary, the Mother of God, with a special honor far higher than that which we give to angels and saints.  (Summary Adapted from the Preface)", "duration": 9311, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "19412", "name": "Luigi Lanzoni"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_2512.jpg", "copyright_year": "1903", "genres": ["Christianity - Commentary"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Ann Boulais"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Ann Boulais"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Ann Boulais"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Temda"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "Preface", "readers": [3681], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_00_lanzoni_64kb.mp3", "duration": 162}, {"section": 1, "title": "Mary's Faith", "readers": [3681], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_01_lanzoni_64kb.mp3", "duration": 540}, {"section": 2, "title": "Mary's Hope", "readers": [3681], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_02_lanzoni_64kb.mp3", "duration": 346}, {"section": 3, "title": "Mary's Love for God", "readers": [3681], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_03_lanzoni_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1485}, {"section": 4, "title": "Mary's Love for the Sacred Humanity of Jesus", "readers": [3681], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/virtuesofmary_2512_librivox/virtuesofmary_04_lanzoni_64kb.mp3", "duration": 292}, {"section": 5, "title": "Mary's Love for the Church", "readers":